Quote:  GiRELLA CYANEA Macleay. <i>Blue-fish; Korokoropounamu.</i> A rare and highly esteemed fish, secured up to 6lb. in deep water off Cape Brett and headlands round Hauraki Gulf. ... Distribution: Unknown south of Hauraki Gulf.
Notes:  Phillipps Notes on the Edible Fishes

